<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Project Introduction</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe, #ffffff, #dbeafe);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #1e293b;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: normal;
      color: #475569;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #334155;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .footer {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #2563eb;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="card">
    <h1><%= projectName %></h1>
    <h2>Project Introduction</h2>

    <p>
      This platform is designed to help users connect, communicate, and grow through
      modern web technologies. It focuses on authentication, real-time interaction,
      skill exchange, and user collaboration in a secure and scalable manner.
    </p>

    <p>
      Built with passion using <span class="highlight">MERN Stack</span>,
      <span class="highlight">Socket.IO</span>, and modern UI practices.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      Created by <span class="highlight"><%= developerName %></span>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
